                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Whisper of Water"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Melody Loop</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/6ce6beac71091e13fe09094e6af6b210_1681263904580471296.png",
                "id": "talent44029",
                "key": "Let the Show Begin♪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Let the Show Begin♪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Heals all of your characters for 4 HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/bae3085f162716c905447f4c84f2bcf8_3343888493374805462.png",
                "id": "talent33929",
                "key": "Shining Miracle♪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Shining Miracle♪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Heal all your characters for 1 HP and your active character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro Application</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4571347647979374372.png",
                "id": "talent13863",
                "key": "Melody Loop",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/2f913e4b976b65b1d93dd9a3606ce58a_7589308178247292584.png",
                "title": "Melody Loop"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_3280134923744742333.png",
                "id": "talent63621",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro Application</span></strong></p><p>When Hydro is applied without dealing any DMG, the Elemental Reaction triggered will ignore DMG-dealing effects:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: No effect</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: No effect</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: The target is unable to perform any Action this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: Creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro/Electro DMG</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4817277211492340826.png",
                "id": "talent2781",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
